column3: Monthly Assessment on Emergency Prevention and Preparedness for COVID-19 in Northeast Nigeria
column4: Hello, my name is --------------------------- and I work with FHI360. We are trying to understand how best to support your community for Health and WASH and COVID response and have a few questions for you.  This interview is private and confidential, and it will not affect receipt of services from FHI360. You are free not to answer any questions you do not want to, and if you do not want to take part in the interview at all, you do not have to and if you feel like you don’t want to continue with the interview we can stop at any time. Your name will not be used. This will take about 30 minutes. Your ideas are important to us – may I ask you a few questions?
